          "reviewBody": "\"Our experience with the school from Stepping Stones to Plus Two has been exceptional.My son thoroughly enjoyed his schooling, as it was filled with engaging activities and fun.The school provided a perfect balance between academics and extracurricular activities. We are grateful for the wonderful journey and the positive impact the school had on him.\"",
