          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "As a parent, the first major decision that one has to take is about your child's schooling. I can sincerely say that enrolling my son at GPS is the best thing that I did. The allround development that the school offers is the best. Apart from the academics and extracurricular skills, they strive to instill values in all the little ones.... Beginning from Stepping Stones, they made it easier for my son to achieve his small and mighty successes... Thank you Global Public School...❤️",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
          "@type": "Review",
