          "datePublished": "2024-07-20",
          "reviewRating": {
            "@type": "Rating",
            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I had the pleasure of visiting Global Public School last year, and I was thoroughly impressed by what I saw. The visionary leadership of the school is evident in every aspect, from the innovative curriculum to the nurturing environment. The culture here is one of excellence and inclusivity, fostering both academic and personal growth. The staff is dedicated and passionate, creating a supportive atmosphere for students. It's clear that Global Public School is committed to shaping future leaders. Highly recommend!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
        {
