            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "My two daughters had a wonderful time studying at GPS. They were amidst a very pleasant cohort of students and I am glad they had good guidance and support from their teachers. The school has a highly accessible and accommodating management and is open to exploring newer avenues to engage both students and faculty.\n\nA shout out to the management and the teachers for enabling strong and meaningful bonds with the kids!",
          "publisher": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "Yellow Slate"
          }
        },
