            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "More than just a place to learn, Global Public School is a caring community that helps students get ready for both academic success and life after school. I fervently urge any parent looking for a school where their child may develop intellectually, socially, and emotionally to consider Global Public School. With its exceptional teachers, encouraging community, and commitment to the full development of students, Global Public School is a model of excellence in education.\nThe Success and Integrity of Global Public School's Leaders, Particularly Jacob Sir, Lakshmi Ma'am and Johan Sir, are more important indicators of the accomplishments of the school. School's spirit of excellence is embodied by their leadership, resilience, and passion, which set a high bar for their peers.",
